         <abstract>
            <p>The iterative process $$a_{n + 1} = (a_n + 3b_n)/4,\quad b_{n + 1} = (\sqrt{a_n b_n} + b_n)/2$$ is studied in detail. The limit of this quadratically converging process is explicitly identified, as are the uniformizing parameters. The role of symbolic computation, in discovering these nontrivial identifications, is highlighted.</p>
          </abstract>
